data.title: Film Forum · PUEBLERINA
data.meta_description:
Pueblerina
(1948, Emilio Fernández) Back from a phony
murder rap, Roberto Cañedo wants nothing
but a simple farming life, despite his love
Columba Domínguez’s child by the man who
falsely turned him in. But amid his own brother’s
tauntings can he
resist...? The last
of Fernández’s
films about village
life. 35mm.
WED, JUNE 10
2:40, 7:00
